data.title: Respiratory Care in Rolla, MO
data.meta_description: Phelps Healthâ€™s Respiratory Therapy Department provides diagnostic and therapeutic services to patients requiring treatment for deficiencies or abnormalities of the respiratory system, from oxygen supplementation to intensive care.
data.text:
The Pulmonary Function Lab at Phelps Health Hospital, located at 1000 West 10th Street in Rolla, offers testing Monday, Tuesday and Thursday.

The Phelps Health Bond Building, located at 600 Blues Lake Parkway in Rolla, offers testing Monday through Wednesday.
